A simple authentication plugin for mediawiki that uses the django
authentication app as a backend.

Requires sessionprofile from http://code.google.com/p/django-login-for-phpbb/

To install copy django-media-authentication/ to extensions/. You
must also modify the login form in includes/templates/UserLogin.php
change name="wpName" to name="username" and name="wpPassword"
to name="password".